This is an example file.

Copy this to a new file named .env (with the dot) and fill in your values.

DO NOT share your .env file or commit it to Git.

--- Discord Bot ---

Paste your bot token from the Discord Developer Portal

DISCORD_TOKEN=YOUR_BOT_TOKEN_GOES_HERE

--- Google AI ---

Paste your API key from ai.google.dev

GEMINI_API_KEY=YOUR_GEMINI_API_KEY_GOES_HERE
GOOGLE_APPLICATION_CREDENTIALS="service-account-key.json"

--- Bot Persona ---

Define how you want the bot to act. Keep it concise.

This is sent to Gemini as a "system instruction".

BOT_PERSONALITY="You are a helpful and witty assistant named Gemini-Bot. You are operating inside a Discord server."

--- Google TTS Voice ---
# Find more voices here: https://cloud.google.com/text-to-speech/docs/voices
# Example: en-US-WaveNet-D (Male), en-US-WaveNet-F (Female), en-US-Studio-M (Male Studio)
TTS_VOICE_NAME="en-GB-Standard-F"